{"tid":1846130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國世界級自私","createTime":"2020-01-27T13:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T15:48:40.000Z","uid":249170,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f633158732de5d177be39c107b9aa9ba5377927d","tid":1846130,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_721667_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_721667_0&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5nlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=49804b76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_721667_0&h=9d2eaeab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_721667_0</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢人和大陸網民，當初得意忘形，在網絡指摘香港人，聲稱香港人警剔武漢肺炎是無事生非、唯恐中國不亂、變相鼓吹港獨。兩三天之後，輪到這種網民呼天搶地、哭爹叫娘。最新的啼哭，見一名武漢大嫂，胸口掛着一個大牌，不滿最高主人習近平主席沒有來武漢視察，疾呼「中央遺棄了我們」。<br />\n<br />\n中國人的基因，百般醜態，可歸納為兩個字，叫做「自私」。<br />\n<br />\n豬年帶着一場政治行為的鼠疫，由武漢開始。此一凶兆沒有一個玄學家事前看得出來。"},{"pid":"ee0c5cec925d5e3a7a80647dce6d66925958400b","tid":1846130,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"現眼報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c8fa4f282972c929e037d992402dea765bef0d","tid":1846130,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"b6fc162f4e33c3a917db943b1972b86ac0f09d7d","tid":1846130,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"yes,中國不嬲都係世界級自私"},{"pid":"b1e92082293c5a7b75d5863082f61cfdede563f1","tid":1846130,"uid":249866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"f9590f014fa9eddddc8c57f5489606dbcf18d0ff","tid":1846130,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsI